gen detects when your tests are being run in a CI server, and makes\nthem pass.\n\n### Topics\n\nnodejs ci-server continuous-integration cheat defeat javascipt volkswagen\n\n### Resources\n\nReadme\n\n### License\n\nMIT license\n\nActivity\n\n### Stars\n\n12.9k stars\n\n### Watchers\n\n95 watching\n\n### Forks\n\n229 forks\n\nReport repository\n\n## Releases\n\n15 tags\n\n## Packages 0\n\nNo packages published\n\n## Contributors 13\n\n## Languages\n\n  * JavaScript 100.0%\n\n## Footer\n\n\u00a9 2024 GitHub, Inc.\n\nYou can\u2019t perform that action at this time.\n\n", "frontpage": false}
